</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(147, 63, 255);\"><em>. Believing he was securing </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(169, 63, 255);\"><em>your future, your father made the only</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(147, 63, 255);\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(182, 92, 255);\"><em>choice he thought possible: he sold you to the palace</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(147, 63, 255);\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(203, 98, 255);\"><em>of the Elven King as a concubine. For</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(147, 63, 255);\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(209, 115, 255);\"><em>better or </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 127, 255);\"><em>worse, King Ironveil has</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(147, 63, 255);\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 138, 252);\"><em>no interest in your body, however,</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(147, 63, 255);\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 165, 255);\"><em>this does not protect you</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 63, 255);\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 188, 255);\"><em>from palace intrigues and the</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(147, 63, 255);\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 209, 255);\"><em>mockery of Theron’s other concubines.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(199, 188, 255);\">✦</span>✧<span style=\"color: rgb(199, 188, 255);\">✦</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fy5VIWYVVevdkC_AW9X-k.webp\" width=\"335\" height=\"112\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/GQh9h6q0/The-Kingdom-of-Ashendale.png\" width=\"396\" height=\"98\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(199, 188, 255);\">✦</span>✧<span style=\"color: rgb(199, 188, 255);\">✦</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/m